but it didn't stop me.

756
00:44:41.560 --> 00:44:43.392
I wanted to be like Uncle Derek.

757
00:44:43.480 --> 00:44:44.515
He sounds like a good bloke.

758
00:44:44.600 --> 00:44:46.830
