for selling drugs to students.

759
00:44:46.920 --> 00:44:47.990
What a cunt.

760
00:44:48.080 --> 00:44:50.390
Probably bought the pedal car
with the proceeds.

761
00:44:50.480 --> 00:44:53.632
Needless to say I never went near it again.
I just let it rust.

762
00:44:53.720 --> 00:44:55.677
But I never forgot
the clear sense of right and wrong

763
00:44:55.760 --> 00:44:57.671
