802
00:47:08.200 --> 00:47:09.713
I'm all right.

803
00:47:12.840 --> 00:47:14.592
I would not wanna be him in the morning.

804
00:47:25.040 --> 00:47:27.998
Well, this is me.

805
00:47:28.560 --> 00:47:32.155
Well, I shall see you in the morning.

806
00:47:32.240 --> 00:47:34.993
