00:47:56.800 --> 00:47:59.997
-When did you move in?
-About five years ago.

812
00:48:01.160 --> 00:48:03.754
-You should get some house plants.
-Oh, yeah, yeah.

813
00:48:03.840 --> 00:48:06.559
