-Everyone knows everyone round here.

872
00:52:06.480 --> 00:52:09.598
Yeah. If you didn't see anything suspicious,
then who did?

873
00:52:14.720 --> 00:52:16.552
It's a bit of a blind spot, I'm afraid.

874
00:52:16.640 --> 00:52:18.790
We just catch the very edge
of the explosion.

875
00:52:18.880 --> 00:52:20.632
Nasty way to go.

876
00:52:20.720 --> 00:52:23.189
-There was something took my eye.
-Really? What's that?

877
00:52:24.000 --> 00:52:26.116
Sandford's most wanted.

878
00:52:26.200 --> 00:52:27.838
(ALL CHEERING)

879
00:52:27.920 --> 00:52:30.196
There you go. It was the swan all along.

880
00:52:30.280 --> 00:52:33.432
-This is not funny, Detective!
