942
00:56:51.960 --> 00:56:54.554
-Accident?
-Just an accident.

943
00:56:55.160 --> 00:56:57.800
It's all right, it's all right.
There's nothing to see.

944
00:56:57.880 --> 00:57:01.555
Come on, everybody. It's all right.
It's just an accident.

945
00:57:09.920 --> 00:57:11.479
FRANK: Nicholas, what is it?

946
00:57:11.560 --> 00:57:15.440
Sir, I think all these deaths are linked.
I think Tim Messenger was murdered.

947
00:57:15.840 --> 00:57:18.878
-Who could do something like this?
-Maybe it was the swan.

948
00:57:18.960 --> 00:57:21.918
-Apparently, they can break a man's arm.
