with Eve Draper.

1294
01:18:51.360 --> 01:18:52.873
And so Eve deserved to die too?

1295
01:18:52.960 --> 01:18:55.270
Well, she did have a very annoying laugh.

1296
01:18:55.360 --> 01:18:56.555
