1402
01:26:52.360 --> 01:26:55.318
Just walk in and arrest the whole village?

1403
01:26:57.000 --> 01:26:58.149
Not exactly.

1404
01:27:29.800 --> 01:27:32.918
Oh, Sergeant Angel?
Someone from London called for you.

1405
01:27:40.680 --> 01:27:42.876
I'll tell them you'll ring them back.

1406
01:27:45.040 --> 01:27:47.111
-Well, that's funny.
-What's that?

1407
01:27:47.560 --> 01:27:50.120
I didn't know we had a mounted division.

1408
01:27:50.200 --> 01:27:51.873
