1411
01:28:18.400 --> 01:28:23.110
AMANDA: Annette, that Sergeant Angel's
back. Check out his horse.

1412
01:28:24.040 --> 01:28:25.917
ANNETTE: (WHISPERS) Roger that!

1413
01:28:27.560 --> 01:28:30.439
-It's...
-Angel.

1414
01:28:32.360 --> 01:28:34.237
