1425
01:32:20.040 --> 01:32:23.590
Stop! Stop this, please!

1426
01:32:24.240 --> 01:32:27.471
Let us stop this mindless violence.

1427
01:32:28.720 --> 01:32:30.631
Nicholas, my son.

1428
01:32:31.720 --> 01:32:35.509
You may not be a man of God,
but surely you're a man of peace.

1429
01:32:35.600 --> 01:32:41.118
I may not be a man of God, Reverend,
but I know right, and I know wrong,

1430
01:32:41.800 --> 01:32:44.269
and I have the good grace
to know which is which.

1431
01:32:44.360 --> 01:32:47.273
Oh, fuck off, Grasshopper.

1432
01:32:48.800 --> 01:32:50.199
No!

1433
01:32:51.360 --> 01:32:53.033
Jesus Christ!

1434
01:32:53.520 --> 01:32:55.431
Nicholas! Nicholas!

1435
01:32:55.960 --> 01:32:57.280
(GASPING)

1436
01:33:01.480 --> 01:33:03.198
